---

<section class="py-24 relative bg-primary text-black overflow-hidden" id="apply">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-5 cta-grid-bg"></div>
  <div class="torn-paper-cta-top"></div>

  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 relative z-10 pt-10">
    <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-16 items-center">
      <!-- Left Column -->
      <div class="lg:w-1/2 text-left relative">
        <div class="absolute -left-16 top-4 hidden xl:block">
          <svg class="w-16 h-16" viewBox="0 0 50 50">
            <path d="M40,40 Q25,25 10,10" fill="none" stroke="black" stroke-width="2"></path>
            <path d="M10,10 L20,12 M10,10 L12,20" fill="none" stroke="black" stroke-width="2"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="inline-block bg-white text-black px-4 py-1 font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-wide mb-6 transform -rotate-1 shadow-lg border border-black rounded-sm relative">
          <span class="material-icons text-xs align-middle mr-1 text-yellow-500">warning</span>⚠️ Solo 2 cupos disponibles este mes
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-6xl font-black font-display uppercase leading-none mb-6">
          Construyamos <br />
          <span class="text-white bg-black px-2 inline-block transform rotate-1 mt-1 border-2 border-black">Algo Único.</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg font-medium mb-8 leading-relaxed opacity-90">
          Deja de perder clientes por una web lenta o genérica. Hablemos sobre tu proyecto y cómo podemos escalar tu facturación digital.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
          <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-2xl font-bold">check_circle</span>
            <span class="font-bold text-sm">Propiedad 100% del código (Sin ataduras)</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-2xl font-bold">bolt</span>
            <span class="font-bold text-sm">Entrega rápida (Sprints de 2 semanas)</span>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-center space-x-3">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-2xl font-bold">payments</span>
            <div>
              <span class="font-bold text-sm block">Inversión desde $1,000 USD</span>
              <span class="text-xs font-medium opacity-80">Ideal para negocios que ya facturan y buscan escalar</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right Column (Form) -->
      <div class="lg:w-1/2 w-full relative">
        <div class="absolute -top-10 -right-4 hidden lg:block transform rotate-6 z-20">
          <span class="font-marker text-2xl text-black">Vamos!</span>
          <svg class="w-10 h-10 inline-block rotate-90" viewBox="0 0 50 50">
            <path d="M10,25 Q25,10 40,25" fill="none" stroke="black" stroke-width="2"></path>
            <path d="M40,25 L30,20 M40,25 L35,15" fill="none" stroke="black" stroke-width="2"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white p-8 border-2 border-black shadow-[8px_8px_0px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,1)] rounded-sm relative z-10 transform rotate-1 transition-transform hover:rotate-0">
          <div class="text-center mb-6">
            <h3 class="text-black font-bold text-2xl font-display">Solicitar Consultoría</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm mt-1">Sin compromiso. Respuesta en &lt; 24h.</p>
          </div>
          <form class="space-y-4">
            <div>
              <label class="block text-gray-700 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider mb-1">Tu Email</label>
              <input
                class="w-full bg-gray-50 border border-gray-300 text-black p-3 rounded-sm focus:ring-0 focus:border-black outline-none transition-colors placeholder-gray-400"
                placeholder="nombre@empresa.com"
                type="email"
              />
            </div>
            <div>
              <label class="block text-gray-700 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider mb-1">Web Actual (Opcional)</label>
              <input
                class="w-full bg-gray-50 border border-gray-300 text-black p-3 rounded-sm focus:ring-0 focus:border-black outline-none transition-colors placeholder-gray-400"
                placeholder="https://tuweb.com"
                type="text"
              />
            </div>
            <div>
              <label class="block text-gray-700 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider mb-1">¿Qué necesitas?</label>
              <select class="w-full bg-gray-50 border border-gray-300 text-black p-3 rounded-sm focus:ring-0 focus:border-black outline-none transition-colors">
                <option>Nueva Landing Page</option>
                <option>Rediseño Web Completo</option>
                <option>Auditoría de Rendimiento</option>
              </select>
            </div>
            <button
              class="w-full bg-black text-white font-bold text-lg py-4 border-2 border-black hover:bg-white hover:text-black transition-all uppercase tracking-wide flex items-center justify-center group mt-4 rounded-sm relative shadow-lg"
              type="button"
            >
              Aplicar para proyecto &gt;
              <span class="absolute top-2 right-2 text-primary">✦</span>
            </button>
          </form>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
